desc-string: Nestled within the lush foliage of the jungle, it's like a miracle on the earth. Its rocky peaks resemble a row of sharp sword blades, yet they also resemble petals.
punishDesc-string: There is a chance to lose 1 piece of equipment as a penalty for failure.

desc-string:
In that shattered domain, a dark fortress stands proudly, its edges suspended amidst the void, devoid of any physical support. It is filled with a large number of dangerous monsters, growing many rare collectibles that have never been seen before.
Recommended team: 3 warriors, 1 collector
punishDesc-string: There is a chance to lose 1 piece of equipment as a penalty for failure.
